title: Unable to start charging session
description: The charging station shows an error when trying to start the session from the app.

title: Payment not processed
description: Payment failed but the charging session was still marked as completed.

title: Incorrect charging history
description: My charging history shows a session that I did not perform.

title: RFID card not working
description: My RFID card is no longer recognized at multiple charging stations.

title: App crashes on startup
description: The mobile app closes immediately after opening on Android.

title: Charging session ended unexpectedly
description: The charging session stops after a few minutes even though the battery is not full.

title: Invoice missing from account
description: I cannot find the invoice for my last charging session in the billing section.

title: Slow response from charging station
description: It takes several minutes before the charging station responds to any command.

title: Wrong tariff applied
description: The price shown for my session does not match the advertised tariff.

title: Account login problem
description: I am unable to log into my account after resetting my password.
